---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="Privacy — Gandía, summer 2026"
	description="How we handle your data. Short version: very little. We only work with the name and contact details you share with us; we never ask for ID, passport or payment information."
	otherLangHref="/es/privacidad/"
	otherLangLabel="Español"
>
	<p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
	<h1>How we handle your <span class="accent">data</span></h1>
	<p class="tagline">
		Short version: very little. Here's exactly what.
	</p>

	<h2>What we collect</h2>
	<p>
		Only what you choose to tell us — your name and contact details (email or phone) through our contact forms, WhatsApp, or email, plus any details about your trip that you'd like to share so we can help plan it.
	</p>

	<h2>What we never ask for</h2>
	<p>
		We will <strong>never</strong> ask for your passport, ID number, card details, bank information or any other sensitive personal data. Bookings and payments are handled entirely by you, directly with the hotels, rental companies and other service providers — those documents live with them, not with us.
	</p>

	<h2>Where it lives</h2>
	<p>
		Contact-form submissions are stored on our <strong>Netlify dashboard</strong>, which only we can access. Messages you send by WhatsApp or email live in those services as you'd expect — WhatsApp's end-to-end encrypted chat, our personal email inboxes. We don't share your details with any third party.
	</p>

	<h2>How long we keep it</h2>
	<p>
		Until your trip is over — and longer if you'd like us to remember your preferences for a return visit. You can ask us to delete your data at any time by writing to <a href="mailto:luizamalik@yahoo.com">luizamalik@yahoo.com</a>; we'll remove it within a few days.
	</p>

	<h2>Analytics</h2>
	<p>
		We use <strong>Google Analytics</strong> to measure visits — how many people come and which pages are popular — purely as aggregate statistics. It sets cookies and sends Google your approximate location, device and browser, and the pages you view. We use <strong>no advertising trackers and no third-party marketing pixels</strong>. See <a href="/cookies/">our cookies page</a> for the detail.
	</p>

	<p class="signoff">Questions? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch.</a></p>

	<style>
		h2 {
			font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin: 2.2rem 0 0.7rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			color: var(--ink);
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
